title: Poor Royals grounds crew member gets eaten by tarp
text:
Poor Royals grounds crew member gets eaten by tarp The Outside Corner 13 hrs ago TOC Locker © Denny Medley-USA TODAY Sports The tarp on the field during a rain delay in game one of the ALDS between the Houston Astros and Kansas City Royals at Kauffman Stadium. Game 1 of the Astros-Royals ALDS was delayed by rain.
AdChoices When putting the tarp on the field, an unfortunate member of Kauffman Stadium’s ground crew was swallowed up by the tarp.
Poor grounds crew... https://t.co/BF84035pCZ
— Joe Lucia (@Joe_TOC) October 9, 2015
